description: The Jivaro Indians, who dwell in the Peruvian forests on the banks of the Rio Napo, conceal a secret that is coveted by many: curaro. The research conducted by scientists from a number of countries triggers an undercurrent of stealthy struggle among the pharmaceutical multinationals, eager to secure for themselves wealth and power. But the Jivaros have no intention of revealing their secret to anyone… The first to come to grief over this is Professor Perez, killed by head hunters. Mister No and Esse-Esse set out on his tracks, acting as guides for Professor Maldonado, who has come from Saõ Paulo, but also for ruthless mercenaries, in the pay of corrupt professor Johnson…
name: Territorio Jivaro

description: Detective Phil Mulligan has gone missing! Only one clue for Mister No and Esse-Esse: a plane ticket to Acalpulco, Mexico… Once they’ve reached the destination, though, our friends get embroiled in an intricate and dangerous affair: what is the starlet Dorothy Lamarr trying to hide? Why are four ruthless cut-throats trying to hunt Mulligan down? Who is it that is prepared to kill in order to get their hands on a roll of film containing photos that ought never to have been taken?… Perhaps, Mister No may need help in the guise of his paper alter ego: Jerry Drake detective!
name: Una Foto che Scotta

description: Whenever CIA agent Hiden is involved, this spells trouble for Mister No. And so, to help his friend Phil Mulligan, Jerry and Esse-Esse are obliged to cross the border and conduct a dangerous investigation among the beautiful homes and the sordid tenements and slums of Los Angeles. A labyrinthine puzzle where all of the protagonists seem to have something to hide or are duping other people by having a double identity… and the unexpected ending will leave everyone with a bitter taste in the mouth!
name: Destinazione Los Angeles

description: District Prosecutor Vargas is a brave and honest man. These are two qualities which, in the small city of San Marcos, in Colombia, can cost you dearly. However, the murder attack in which he loses his life risks turning into a further indictment for the narcotics traffickers he was fighting, since chance places Vargas’s secretary, the attractive and courageous Helena Sánchez, as well as Jorge Almeida, his bodyguard who actually survived the attack, on the path of a certain gringo who just can’t seem to stay out of trouble: Jerry Drake, better known as Mister No!
name: L'Attentato

description: The documents that have gotten into the hands of District Attorney Vargas – testifying to collusion between Columbian narcotics traffickers and men in the corridors of power - could lead to the most extraordinary political upheaval... That’s why Vargas has been brutally killed, and that’s why the masterminds behind his murder now have to stop his PA, Helena, his bodyguard, Jorge, and a gringo in search of trouble, Mister No. And the killers will resort to any means whatsoever to prevent our men from getting to Medellín. But they’re dealing with much smarter people than they expected...
name: Gli Intrighi del Potere

description: Piotr Van de Veer met Esse-Esse in the Far East, when our “CRUCCO” decided to go out there, at the end of the war, and spend time in those exotic landscapes. Now our friends meet up again many years on in Caracas, where Van De Veer has come to purchase weapons. But to cover him and make sure he gets by unnoticed, Esse-Esse and Mister No will have to take a huge risk…
name: Trafficanti di Morte

description: A top-secret load of weapons is triggering a struggle among gun-runners. Embroiled in the sordid intrigue, Mister No, Esse-Esse and his long-lost friend Van de Veer seem to have no other hope of escape than a getaway on the San Vincente, a cargo ship that’s going to cross the Pacific Ocean… Destination: the Far-East, which will provide the backdrop of a whole year of new exotic adventures for our Jerry!
name: Indocina

description: The armaments brought in by Van De Veer, with the aid of Mister No and Esse-Esse, are a coveted target for many people in the Laotian region of Xieng Kuhang. Wise old Phan Bai wants the weaponry to protect his peasants against the fury of the Hmong revels, whilst the son of the big absentee landowner, the ambitious Zhou, would prefer to use them to boost his own power. And Mister No and Esse-Esse are bang in the midst of all this, ready to side with a people who seem to be without hope...
name: Il Sentiero dei Ricordi

description: Before the Second World War, Colonel Moong Fat, a Chinese warlord, had embarked on an ambitious project: a railroad that would cross the immense expanses of jungle to connect China with Laos. The project was interrupted, but now Chartered Engineer Maartens has decided to complete it. The engineer’s guides and bodyguards, in that wild region, will be Mister No, Esse-Esse and Van de Veer!
name: Il Risveglio del Drago

description: For Mister No, Esse-Esse and Van de Veer, their new job as guides in the Laos jungle is hardly going to be a piece of cake. Not only will the perils of nature and a danger made of fangs and claws slow down the reconstruction of the railroad, but an unexpected development will completely overturn the course of events...
name: Tracce di Sangue

description: It’s time for the showdown! Mister No, Esse-Esse and Van de Veer, caught up as they are in the crossfire between the Laotian army and the rebels of the North headed by the diabolical Taifun, must somehow dodge this mortal trap. And even Alexandra Maartens will risk losing her life when she discovers she’s been duped…
name: Gli Ultimi Fuochi

description: A BRIGHTEST DAY tie-in! Exploding out of BLACKEST NIGHT comes the next exciting chapter in the Green Lantern mythos: "New Guardians"! Forced together during the rise of the Black Lanterns, Hal Jordan, Sinestro, Carol Ferris, Saint Walker, Atrocitus, Indigo-1 and Larfleeze must agree to disagree if their next mission is to succeed. But when one of the strangest beings from Green Lantern's past returns, the future of the Lanterns and the universe at large once again falls into question.
name: The New Guardians, Chapter 1

description: Eisner-nominee and incoming WONDER WOMAN writer J.
